text: Isaković () is a South Slavic patronymic surname derived from a masculine given name Isak (Isaac). It may refer to: *Alija Isaković (1932–1997), writer *Antonije Isaković (1923–2002), writer *Boris Isaković (born 1966), actor *Branko Isaković (born 1958), musician *Mile Isaković (born 1958), handball player *Mirjana Isaković (born 1936), artist *Sara Isaković (1988), swimmer *Vuk Isaković (1696–1759), military commander Category:Bosnian-language surnames Category:Serbian-language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames
title: Isaković
